AND &amp;lt;lora:Luna3.0:0.8&amp;gt;,  luna_sakurakouji\(navel\), (red eyes:1.2), long hair, bangs, collared shirt, shirt, hair bow, bow, hair between eyes, floating hair, upper body, very long hair, grey hair, white shirt, black bow, ribbon, dress, hair ribbon
